{"experienceId":"draft-2931f0b0-2581-4150-9e3a-cf380be16969","title":"第二个视频-da49","contentVersion":"draft.302a0f50aa8e","mediaFingerprint":"sha256:302a0f50aa8e6de7b53ebcfaa5a8922bc2fd2f8d295fff085d52a22e0ea8ac4a","publishStatus":"draft","blockers":["HUMAN_REVIEW_REQUIRED"],"evidence":[{"evidenceId":"asr-dea47a506ca79e64","startMs":120,"endMs":2680,"text":"哪个国家印出了这张100万亿元的钞票？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-5eb8b7738115c9e8","startMs":3870,"endMs":6110,"text":"我跟你说，它的通货膨胀可以说是世界闻名。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-dc8a957e2015ea4e","startMs":6190,"endMs":8150,"text":"从2000年开始，通胀就没下过三位数。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-d590bd247c6f9011","startMs":8710,"endMs":12430,"text":"而伴随着这个恶性通胀的，其实就是金圆对美元的急速贬值。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-9bf7faa9f3d790d4","startMs":12550,"endMs":17990,"text":"98年的时候，一美元还能兑24津巴布韦元，到06年就贬值到一美元兑10万金元。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-90564eb254e82ffe","startMs":18070,"endMs":19310,"text":"这津巴布韦政府一看，对吧？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-0cf76a96946f8bd8","startMs":19310,"endMs":28390,"text":"这0也太多了，干脆咱就抹掉3个0，定义一个新的津巴布韦元，叫 ZWN 啊，它原来那个货币叫 ZWD 这样一美元就兑100金元了，对吧？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-be347275e58eae22","startMs":28430,"endMs":28630,"text":"你看。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-474874296f7c7913","startMs":28850,"endMs":29290,"text":"多聪明！"},{"evidenceId":"asr-90a1ea618645796d","startMs":29490,"endMs":33850,"text":"结果津巴布韦这边没止住恶性的通货膨胀，这津元贬值的速度就越来越快。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-3386e193fbff948d","startMs":33930,"endMs":40530,"text":"一年后07年4月的时候，又跌到了1美元兑3万津巴布韦元，年底的时候又变成1美元兑200万津元。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-511788a679c6343f","startMs":40610,"endMs":44650,"text":"之后每个月都在狂泻，半年之后就出现了那张5000亿津元的钞票。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-876a47d7a6cbc9c9","startMs":44730,"endMs":46970,"text":"津巴布韦政府一看，这0又太多了，对吧？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-b116496799add813","startMs":47010,"endMs":54000,"text":"老办法，再抹0，这次直接抹掉10个0，就是除以100亿，然后这新的货币呢，就叫做 ZWR 好吧。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-9cfefbcd8db1e4de","startMs":54080,"endMs":59080,"text":"这个时候啊，津巴布韦通货膨胀，据估算已经飙升到了9%×10的22次方。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-4ddc82ed315b965c","startMs":59160,"endMs":65720,"text":"那外汇市场可想而知，到半年之后，就09年初的时候，他会印出来那张举世闻名的一百万亿津元的钞票。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-1ffa0d178548ee8d","startMs":66370,"endMs":69610,"text":"不过你看着这么多万亿，最后其实也就值不到0.4美元。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-be84958f84ca0370","startMs":69610,"endMs":77930,"text":"那央行说好，咱再去掉12个零，再除以一万亿，啊，这个新的货币就叫 ZWL 你看，短短三年里头，津巴布韦政府已经砍掉了25个零。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-d3da8ac91fa5e229","startMs":78050,"endMs":80050,"text":"到最后这津元已经完全没有信用了。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-16b11880ed09861a","startMs":80050,"endMs":84450,"text":"你想你这政府整天这么砍零，然后推出新货币，到最后可能这26个字母都不够你用。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-a314d745bbf083ca","startMs":84570,"endMs":89250,"text":"无奈之下，政府被迫放弃津元，改用欧元、美元，这才止住了国内的恶性通胀。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-ea610d96501a38ec","startMs":89330,"endMs":89850,"text":"不过最近哈。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-2718ae832738e0c2","startMs":90040,"endMs":95000,"text":"刚缓过来一点，19年的时候津巴布韦又活分起来了，推出了自己的货币，通胀又飙到三位数。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-6c8e3de1973b604d","startMs":95040,"endMs":103120,"text":"然后今年4月份，它就又又又推出自己的新货币，叫 ZWG 津巴布韦金，这回号称是有贵金属背书，你就说这津巴布韦它乱不乱？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-c0079408b2c75694","startMs":103880,"endMs":108080,"text":"咱就通过这个极端的例子哈，你其实非常容易看出来，通货膨胀跟外汇之间的关系。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-8ae883595281ffb8","startMs":108200,"endMs":112760,"text":"物价它对汇率的影响最底层，但它同时也可能会非常的缓慢，非常的隐形。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-3cadaa710acee716","startMs":112880,"endMs":121880,"text":"所以你如果一般看那种比较主流的货币哈，你就比如说美元，过去50年通货膨胀跟汇率的对比，只有80年代美国高速通胀的时期，你才能非常明显的看到负相关。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-e020c521d91a27f8","startMs":121920,"endMs":124440,"text":"从90年代之后，就没有什么特别明显的相关性。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-85ef223232d0f920","startMs":124480,"endMs":125080,"text":"这为什么啊？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-ba9574e932980847","startMs":125120,"endMs":132240,"text":"就是因为像美元、欧元、日元，包括人民币，它大部分的时间通胀都是在10%以下，这个区间叫轻微的波动。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-d88ad7c104916a7f","startMs":132280,"endMs":139760,"text":"你要不是放到像什么津巴布韦、委内瑞拉、土耳其这种通胀一下就飙到超过50%的这些国家，一般看起来啊，可能都不会那么明显。"}],"concepts":[{"conceptId":"c1","name":"100万亿津巴布韦元纸币（2009年初）","firstMentionMs":120,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-dea47a506ca79e64","asr-4ddc82ed315b965c"]},{"conceptId":"c2","name":"津巴布韦恶性通货膨胀","firstMentionMs":3870,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-5eb8b7738115c9e8","asr-dc8a957e2015ea4e"]},{"conceptId":"c3","name":"津元对美元的急速贬值","firstMentionMs":8710,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-d590bd247c6f9011"]},{"conceptId":"c4","name":"货币重新面额化（砍零/换名）","firstMentionMs":19310,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-0cf76a96946f8bd8","asr-b116496799add813","asr-be84958f84ca0370"]},{"conceptId":"c5","name":"津元完全丧失信用","firstMentionMs":78050,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-d3da8ac91fa5e229","asr-16b11880ed09861a"]},{"conceptId":"c6","name":"通货膨胀与外汇的底层关系","firstMentionMs":103880,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-c0079408b2c75694","asr-8ae883595281ffb8"]},{"conceptId":"c7","name":"主流货币的低通胀区间（<10%）","firstMentionMs":125120,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-ba9574e932980847"]},{"conceptId":"c8","name":"极端通胀国家（津巴布韦/委内瑞拉/土耳其，通胀>50%）","firstMentionMs":132280,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-d88ad7c104916a7f"]}],"claims":[{"claimId":"cl1","statement":"自2000年起，津巴布韦年通胀率从未低于三位数（百位数百分比的恶性通胀）。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-dc8a957e2015ea4e"]},{"claimId":"cl2","statement":"1998年 1美元 ≈ 24 津巴布韦元（ZWD）。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-9bf7faa9f3d790d4"]},{"claimId":"cl3","statement":"2006年 1美元 ≈ 100,000 ZWD（津元对美元已大幅贬值）。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-9bf7faa9f3d790d4"]},{"claimId":"cl4","statement":"2006年津巴布韦实施首次换币：抹掉3个零，推出新货币ZWN，1美元 ≈ 100 ZWN。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-0cf76a96946f8bd8"]},{"claimId":"cl5","statement":"2007年4月 1美元 ≈ 30,000 ZWN（一年内几乎贬值300倍）。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-3386e193fbff948d"]},{"claimId":"cl6","statement":"2007年底 1美元 ≈ 2,000,000 ZWN（约半年后出现5000亿ZWN面额钞票）。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-3386e193fbff948d","asr-511788a679c6343f"]},{"claimId":"cl7","statement":"2008年7月津巴布韦再次换币：抹掉10个零（除以100亿），新货币为ZWR。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-b116496799add813"]},{"claimId":"cl8","statement":"2008年津巴布韦通胀据估算飙升至约 9×10²² %（天文级恶性通胀）。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-9cfefbcd8db1e4de"]},{"claimId":"cl9","statement":"2009年初发行的100万亿津元钞票实际价值不到0.4美元。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-1ffa0d178548ee8d","asr-4ddc82ed315b965c"]},{"claimId":"cl10","statement":"三年内津巴布韦政府已累计砍掉约25个零，并推出ZWL。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-be84958f84ca0370"]},{"claimId":"cl11","statement":"恶性通胀后政府被迫放弃津元、改用欧元与美元做记账货币，本国恶性通胀才被止住。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-a314d745bbf083ca"]},{"claimId":"cl12","statement":"2019年津巴布韦重新推出本币，通胀再次飙到三位数。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-2718ae832738e0c2"]},{"claimId":"cl13","statement":"视频发布年4月津巴布韦推出新货币 ZWG（“津巴布韦金”），号称有贵金属背书。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"insufficient","evidenceIds":["asr-6c8e3de1973b604d"]},{"claimId":"cl14","statement":"物价（通胀）对汇率的影响是“最底层”的，但通常很缓慢、很隐形。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-8ae883595281ffb8"]},{"claimId":"cl15","statement":"在过去50年的美元数据里，只有80年代美国高通胀时期，美元通胀与汇率能明显看到负相关。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-3cadaa710acee716"]},{"claimId":"cl16","statement":"1990年代以后，主流货币的通胀与汇率之间已没有特别明显的相关性。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"conflict","evidenceIds":["asr-e020c521d91a27f8","asr-85ef223232d0f920"]},{"claimId":"cl17","statement":"美元、欧元、日元、人民币大部分时间通胀都低于10%，处于“轻微波动”区间。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"support_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-ba9574e932980847"]}],"causalEdges":[{"edgeId":"e1","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c2"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c3"},"mechanism":"国内物价持续飙升侵蚀本币购买力，相对美元的需求下降导致津元对美元急速贬值。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-d590bd247c6f9011"]},{"edgeId":"e2","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c3"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c4"},"mechanism":"当货币面值零数过多、会计与日常使用不便时，政府通过“砍零/换名”进行重新面额化以缓解表观问题。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-0cf76a96946f8bd8","asr-90564eb254e82ffe","asr-876a47d7a6cbc9c9","asr-b116496799add813"]},{"edgeId":"e3","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c_renomination_zwn"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"cl_devaluation_accelerates"},"mechanism":"重新面额化后恶性通胀并未被遏制，津元对美元的贬值速度反而越来越快。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-90a1ea618645796d","asr-3386e193fbff948d"]},{"edgeId":"e4","from":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"cl_devaluation_accelerates"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c_zwl_credibility_loss"},"mechanism":"反复重新面额化和持续贬值导致津元完全丧失了信用。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-d3da8ac91fa5e229"]},{"edgeId":"e5","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c5"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"cl11"},"mechanism":"本币信用崩塌后，政府放弃发行主权货币，转而直接使用欧元、美元作为流通手段，从而切断通胀传导。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-a314d745bbf083ca"]},{"edgeId":"e6","from":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"cl17"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"cl16"},"mechanism":"在通胀长期低于10%的轻微波动区间，汇率更多被利差、资本流动、增长差等因素主导，物价对汇率的信号被淹没。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-ba9574e932980847","asr-e020c521d91a27f8"]},{"edgeId":"e7","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c6"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"c8"},"mechanism":"当通胀极端化（>50%），购买力平价效应被放大，通胀-汇率的负相关才在图形上“肉眼可见”。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-c0079408b2c75694","asr-d88ad7c104916a7f"]}],"conditions":[{"conditionId":"cond1","variable":"inflation_rate","operator":"above","threshold":50,"unit":"%","affectsEdgeId":"e7","statement":"当一个国家的年通胀率持续显著超过50%（如津巴布韦、委内瑞拉、土耳其），通胀与本币汇率的负相关才会直观可见。","evidenceIds":["asr-d88ad7c104916a7f"]},{"conditionId":"cond2","variable":"inflation_rate","operator":"below","threshold":10,"unit":"%","affectsEdgeId":"e6","statement":"当主流货币（美元/欧元/日元/人民币）的年通胀率长期低于10%，处于“轻微波动”区间，通胀与汇率的统计相关性通常不显著。","evidenceIds":["asr-ba9574e932980847","asr-e020c521d91a27f8"]}],"triggerCandidates":[],"rejectedTriggerCandidates":[{"candidateId":"cue-ev15","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev7","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev11","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev12","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev1","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev6","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev2","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev10","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev13","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev4","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev8","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev3","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev5","reason":"PAYLOAD_UNAUTHORABLE"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev9","reason":"PAYLOAD_UNAUTHORABLE"},{"candidateId":"cue-ev14","reason":"PAYLOAD_UNAUTHORABLE"}],"approvedTriggers":[]}